+The config is validated with `validateWritTypeConfig` before registration. Errors propagate as plain `Error` with the prefix `[clerk] writTypeConfig.<path>:`. Throws on:
+- Duplicate registration (same type name already registered).
+- Post-seal registration (called after `phase:started`).
+- Invalid config (validator errors propagate verbatim).
