+Once registered, writs of this type can be posted, transitioned, and classified using the full ClerkApi. Every transition is validated against the type's declared `allowedTransitions`; posting the type works immediately.
+
+The registration window closes when `phase:started` fires (after all apparatus have started). Registrations after that point throw with `registration window has closed`.
 
